id: pm-lkd7
title: "CI: smaller matrix on PRs, full matrix on main push only"
description: "PRs currently spin all 5 matrix entries (3 OS x Node 20 + Node 22 + Node 24 on Ubuntu). Trade off PR breadth for speed: PRs run only ubuntu/node20 + macos/node20 (catch cross-OS quickly); main push runs full 5-entry matrix. Saves 2 runner jobs per PR push, ~20min total runner minutes per PR cycle."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[4]: ci,matrix,performance,pm-cli
